    "story.quest1_1.line01": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "昼休みの教室。窓の外は青空、鳥の声が響いている。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "午休的教室里，窗外湛蓝的天空与鸟鸣交织。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "It's lunch break; blue sky and birdsong spill through the classroom windows."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest1_1.line02": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ねぇ、今日の理科の授業、聞いてた？"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "喂，你有好好听今天的理科课吗？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Hey, were you even listening in science class today?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest1_1.line03": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "地震の話、ちょっと怖くない？"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "地震的内容，听起来有点可怕吧？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "That earthquake talk was kind of scary, right?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest1_1.line04": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "うん、でも先生が言ってた『地球の呼吸』って言葉、なんかロマンチックじゃない？"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "嗯，可老师说的“地球的呼吸”这词儿，还挺浪漫的不是吗？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Yeah, but when the teacher called it the \"Earth's breath,\" it sounded kind of romantic, didn't it?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest1_1.line05": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ロマンチックって...（笑）やっぱりあんた、変わってるよ。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "浪漫什么啦（笑）。你果然还是那么怪。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Romantic? Seriously? (laughs) You're such a weirdo."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest1_1.line06": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "でも、地球が生きてるみたいで面白いかもね。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "不过，地球好像活着，其实也挺有趣的。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Still, imagining Earth as a living thing is kind of interesting."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest1_1.line07": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ねぇ、もし本当に地球が“呼吸”してるなら、僕たちはその上で暮らしてる小さな生き物かも。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "要是真的地球在“呼吸”，我们就像住在它身上的小生物吧。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "If it's really breathing, we're just tiny creatures living on top of it."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest1_1.line08": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "まあ、地球が呼吸していようがしていまいが、私たちはそもそも小さな生き物なんだよね。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "不管地球呼不呼吸，我们本来就是小不点啦。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Breathe or not, we're already specks to begin with."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest1_1.line09": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "……って、あれ？ちょっと揺れてない？"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "……咦？你感觉到晃了吗？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "...Huh? Did it just shake?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest1_1.line10": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "そうだね、でももっと待ったら止まるでしょう。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "是有点，不过等等就会停吧。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Yeah, but it'll stop if we wait a bit, right?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest1_1.line11": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "あれ……また止まってないか……"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "咦……怎么还没停……"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Wait... why isn't it stopping...?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest1_1.line12": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "うわ！本棚が倒れた！"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "哇！书柜倒了！"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Whoa! The bookshelf fell!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest1_1.line13": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "わっ、うそ！？　こんな強いの、初めて――！"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "不会吧！？这么大的我还是第一次——！"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "No way!? I've never felt it this strong—!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest1_1.line14": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "机の下に！　早く！"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "钻到桌子下面！快！"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Get under the desks! Hurry!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest1_1.line15": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "rumble_stop"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "【震动渐止】"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "[The shaking subsides.]"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest1_1.line16": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "揺れはどんどん強くなり、黒板が倒れ、天井のライトが落ちてくる。教室中が悲鳴で満ちる。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "摇晃越来越剧烈，黑板倒下，吊灯砸落，教室里充满尖叫。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The tremor grows wilder—blackboards crash down, ceiling lights shatter, and screams fill the room."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest1_1.line17": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "キャー！　天井が！　助けてぇっ！"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "呀——！天花板！救命啊！"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Kyaa! The ceiling! Somebody help!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest1_1.line18": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "こっちのドアが開かない！誰かっ！"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这边的门打不开！谁来帮忙！"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "This door won't open! Somebody!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest1_1.line19": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "激しい衝撃音。窓ガラスが砕け散り、壁が崩れ始める。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "巨大的冲击声炸开，玻璃碎裂，墙壁开始崩塌。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "A violent crash erupts; windows shatter and the walls begin to crumble."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest1_1.line20": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "いやっ……！"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "不要啊……！"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "No...!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest1_1.line21": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "その瞬間、天井の一部が落下し、みなとの肩をかすめた。彼女は小さく呻いて、そのまま意識を失う。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "就在那一刻，天花板的一块砸落，擦过美奈的肩膀，她闷哼一声便失去意识。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "In that instant, a slab from the ceiling grazes Minato's shoulder; she cries out and collapses unconscious."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest1_1.line22": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "みなと！？　しっかりして！　みなと！"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "美奈！？撑住！美奈！"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Minato!? Hang on! Minato!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest1_1.line23": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "主人公は震える手で彼女の手を強く握りしめた。轟音の中、心臓の鼓動だけがはっきりと聞こえる。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "主角握紧颤抖的手。轰鸣之中，他只能清楚听见自己的心跳。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "His hands shaking, the protagonist grips hers. Amid the roar, only his heartbeat rings clear."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest1_1.line24": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "（……助けたい。どうか、誰か……！）"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "（……想救她。谁来……！）"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "(I have to save her. Someone, please...!)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest1_1.line25": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "その瞬間、主人公の手から眩しい光が溢れ出した。崩壊する教室が白い閃光に包まれる。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "就在那一瞬，主角的手心迸出耀眼白光，崩塌的教室被刺眼的闪光吞没。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Then, a blinding light erupts from his hand, swallowing the collapsing classroom."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest1_2.line01": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "視界がねじれ、音が遠ざかる。次に目を開けたとき――そこは見知らぬ白い施設だった。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "视野扭曲，声音远去。再次睁眼时，眼前是陌生的白色设施。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sight warps and sound fades. When {name} opens their eyes again, they're inside a stark white facility."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest1_2.line02": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ここ……どこ？　みなと……！　大丈夫か？"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这里……是哪？美奈……！你没事吧？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Where... are we? Minato...! Are you okay?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest1_2.line03": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "……う、うん……。ここ……学校じゃないよね……？"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "……嗯，嗯……这里……不是学校吧……？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "...Y-yeah... This isn't school, is it...?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest1_2.line04": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "はっと顔を上げると、目の前に男が立っていた。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "抬头一看，眼前站着一名男子。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "He looks up to see a man standing before them."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest1_2.line05": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "......"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "......"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "......"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest1_2.line06": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ここって...?"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这里是……？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "And this place is...?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest1_2.line07": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "G-Labへようこそ"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "欢迎来到G-Lab。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Welcome to G-Lab."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line01": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "白い部屋の中、無数のモニターが青く光っている。機械の低い唸りが、静寂の中に響いていた。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "G-Lab里灯光冰冷闪烁。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Inside the white room, countless monitors glow blue while machinery hums in the stillness."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line02": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "落ち着いた？　ここはG-Lab――地質学と地殻変動を研究する施設だ。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这里是G-Lab，研究地质活动。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Calm down. This is G-Lab—a facility dedicated to geology and crustal shifts."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line03": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "研究所だって言ってたけど……もう帰っていいのかな。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "You call it a lab... so can we go home now?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line04": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "そうね。帰す前に、ひとつだけ見てほしい映像があるの。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "先看个影像。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "You can, but first I need you to see a video."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line05": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Kaedeがリモコンを押すと、壁面のモニターにニュース映像が映し出された。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Kaede presses a remote and news footage flares onto the wall."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line06": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "『速報です。仙台市中心部で観測された地震により、多数の建物が倒壊。現在も余震が続いています――』"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "新闻：仙台地震严重，余震仍在持续。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"Breaking news: a quake in downtown Sendai has toppled numerous buildings, and aftershocks continue—\""
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line07": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "……そんな……これ、私たちの街……？"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "那是我们的城市……"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "No way... that's our city, isn't it...?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line08": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "……家、大丈夫かな……母さん……！"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "...Is my house okay...? Mom...!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line09": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "主人公はポケットからスマホを取り出す。だが、その瞬間――スマホが震えた。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "He fumbles for his phone, which starts to vibrate."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line10": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "え……！？　母さんから……！"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "妈妈来电。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Huh...!? It's Mom...!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line11": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "phone_call"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "[Incoming call]"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line12": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "もしもし！？　あんた無事なの！？　ニュース見て心配で……！"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "妈妈：你们没事吧？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Hello!? Are you okay!? I saw the news and nearly panicked to death...!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line13": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "うん！　俺も無事！　今、避難してて……！　母さんの方こそ！？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Yeah! I'm safe! I'm taking shelter... Are you alright!?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line14": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "家は少し壊れたけど、なんとか大丈夫。ほんとによかった……！"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "家里有些损伤，但人都安全。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The house took some damage, but we're alright. I'm so relieved...!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line15": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "安堵の笑みが浮かぶ。しばしの沈黙のあと、母の声が柔らかくなった。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Relief softens her voice after a brief silence."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line16": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "すぐ帰っておいで。今どこにいるの？"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "快回来，你现在在哪？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Come home soon, okay? Where are you?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line17": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "主人公が口を開こうとした瞬間、Kaedeが静かに歩み寄り、スマホを手に取った。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Just as he opens his mouth, Kaede steps in and gently takes the phone."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line18": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "えっ、ちょ、Kaedeさん！？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "H-hey, Kaede!?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line19": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "――もしもし、失礼します。こちら、G-Labの研究員・Kaedeと申します。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "楓：我是G-Lab的研究员。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "—Hello, pardon the intrusion. I'm Kaede, a researcher at G-Lab."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line20": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "え？　あ、はい……？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Uh? I-I see...?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line21": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "実は、お子さんが先ほどの地震の際に、特殊な反応を示しました。私たちはその原因を調べるため、短期間の協力をお願いしたいのです。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "她解释我有特殊反应，想请我短期协助。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "During the quake your child exhibited an unusual response. We'd like to request short-term cooperation to investigate."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line22": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "えっ、そんな……中学生の子に研究を……？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "What? You want a middle-schooler involved in research...?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line23": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "もちろん安全な環境で行います。今後の地震防止にもつながる可能性があります。もし彼の“感覚”が地殻変動と関係しているなら、命を救えるかもしれません。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "她强调安全和防灾意义。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "It will be in a controlled environment. This could help prevent future quakes. If his \"sense\" ties to crustal changes, it might save lives."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line24": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Kaedeの声は落ち着いていたが、その奥に切実な熱があった。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Kaede's tone stays calm, yet earnest heat seeps through."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line25": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "……そんな大事なことなら……でも、本当に危険じゃないんですね？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "...If it's that important... but it won't be dangerous, right?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line26": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ええ、約束します。食事も宿泊もこちらで責任を持って管理します。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Rest assured, we'll take full responsibility for his safety and accommodations."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line27": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "短い沈黙のあと、母のため息が聞こえた。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "After a pause, his mother's sigh comes through."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line28": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "……わかりました。でも、ちゃんと休ませてあげてくださいね。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "好吧，但一定要让他休息。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "...Alright. But please let him rest properly."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line29": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ありがとうございます。責任をもってお預かりします。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Thank you. We'll take good care of him."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line30": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Kaedeがスマホを主人公に返す。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Kaede hands the phone back."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line31": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "…………えっ。ちょっと、何が起きたんですか。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": ".........Uh. Wait, what just happened?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line32": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "お母さん、話が早い……（笑）"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Your mom's surprisingly quick on the uptake. (laughs)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line33": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "うちの親、意外とノリいいな！？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "I didn't know my parents would agree that fast!?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line34": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ふふ、助かりました。ではこれから、よろしくね。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Heh, that helps. We'll be counting on you."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line35": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "そして、二人に今後のやることを説明するする。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "她开始说明任务。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Now then, let me explain what comes next."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line36": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Kaedeは二人に装置を差し出した。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Kaede hands them a pair of devices."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line37": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "これは“地質ハンマー”。サンプル採集用のツールよ。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "地质锤：用来采样。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "This is a rock hammer for collecting samples."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line38": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "そして――これが“フェーズシフター”。君の能力を安定化させる。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "相位转换器：用来稳定能力。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "And this is the Phase Shifter—it stabilizes your ability."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line39": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "フェーズシフター……？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Phase Shifter...?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line40": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "要は、君の空間移動を制御する装置。これを使えば、G-Labと外界の行き来が安全にできるわ。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "它能控制传送，往返更安全。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "In short, it keeps your spatial hops under control so you can travel safely between G-Lab and outside."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line41": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "って、つまり私たち今後本当に地質研究活動をやるか...。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "也就是说，要开始地质调查了。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "So we're really going to be doing geo research now..."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line42": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "もちろん、みんなを助けられる仕事だよ……もしかしてできない？。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Of course; it's a job that saves lives... What's wrong, not up for it?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line43": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "は？そんなわけないだろ！。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Huh? Not happening!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line44": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "うわ、Kaedeさんの挑発に弱いね。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Wow, Kaede knows exactly how to rile you up."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line45": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ふふ、やる気が出たならそれでいいわ。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Heh, as long as you're motivated."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest2_1.line46": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "じゃ初めての任務が始めるわ、地質ハンマーで薄片サンプルを採集しよう。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "第一项任务：用地质锤采薄片样本。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Then let's kick off your first mission: use the rock hammer to collect thin-section samples."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_1.line01": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "準備したか？じゃフェーズシフターを使ってみて。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "先试试相位转换器。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ready? Then try using the Phase Shifter."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_1.line02": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "本当に役に立てるかこれ…自分の人身安全を心配している。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Is this really going to help...? I'm more worried about staying alive."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_1.line03": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "やはりびびっているね。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Knew you'd chicken out."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_1.line04": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "大丈夫だよ、俺とお母さんと約束でしょう、安全を確保って。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Relax. I promised you and your mom we'd keep you safe."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_1.line05": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ああ、わかったよ……行くしかないな。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "好吧，那就开始。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Alright, alright... guess I'm doing this."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_1.line06": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "フェーズシフターを使いなさい"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "转换器启动。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Activate the Phase Shifter."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_2.line01": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "再び目を開ける時、{name}はもう野外にいた。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "{name}抵达野外。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "When {name} opens their eyes again, they're already outdoors."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_2.line02": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "無事に到着したね、じゃ採集任務を始めよ"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "You arrived safely. Let's start the collection mission."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_2.line03": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "地面上の指示を見えるか、それを従って、目的地でサンプルを採集しよう"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "看指引，到目标点采样。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "See the markers on the ground? Follow them and grab the samples."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_3.line01": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "荒れ果てた地表に風が吹き抜ける。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "地表一片荒芜。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Wind scours the desolate ground."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_3.line02": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "{name}は小さな機材ケースを背負い、山のふもとの露頭に立っていた。通信端末のライトが点滅し、研究室とつながる。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "{name} stands at the outcrop near the mountain base, gear case on their back as the terminal light flickers to connect with the lab."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_3.line03": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "こちらラボ。音声、映ってるか？風が強いみたいだね。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "实验室，画面和声音正常吗？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lab here. Audio and video okay? Sounds windy over there."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_3.line04": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "はい、聞こえてます。こっちはまだちょっと砂ぼこりが舞ってます。空も灰色で…地震のあとって感じです。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "收到，这里像地震后的现场。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Loud and clear. Still a bit dusty, and the sky's gray... definitely feels post-quake."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_3.line05": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "映像きたきた。うわ、泥だらけじゃん。長靴はいてきた？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Feed's up. Whoa, you're covered in mud. Did you bring rubber boots?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_3.line06": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "……はいたけど、もう半分沈みました。あー、これ洗うの大変だなあ。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "...I did, but I'm already ankle-deep. Ugh, washing these will be a pain."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_3.line07": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ほらほら。そこが震源に一番近い露頭だからね。サンプルを頼むよ。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Focus. That's the closest outcrop to the hypocenter, so get us a sample."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_3.line08": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "{name}は地質ハンマーを取り出し、慎重に岩の表面を叩く。乾いた音が風の中に消える。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "{name}用地质锤取样。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "{name} pulls out the rock hammer, tapping carefully as the dry clinks vanish into the wind."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_3.line09": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "主人公はしゃがみ込み、岩の割れ目から慎重に破片を取り出した。小さなケースに入れながら、どこかでカラスの鳴き声が響く。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "He crouches, prying fragments from the fissure into small cases while a crow caws somewhere in the distance."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_3.line10": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "おっ、きれいな層だね。粉っぽくなってるところがある。なんかお菓子のクッキーみたい。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ooh, look at those bands. That powdery part totally looks like crushed cookies."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_3.line11": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "地面スイーツか…。でも、手で触るとちょっと柔らかい。石のはずなのに。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Earth desserts, huh... but it feels kinda soft for rock."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_3.line12": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "それは興味深いね。地震で砕けた部分かもしれない。持ち帰って薄片にしてみよう。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "像是震碎的部位，先带回去。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Interesting. Might be what shattered during the quake. Bring it back for thin sections."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_3.line13": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "サンプルケースを閉じたその瞬間、地面が低く唸った。風が止み、空気が一気に重くなる。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "地面传来低沉的轰鸣。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "As the case clicks shut, the ground lets out a low groan. The wind dies, and the air turns heavy."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_3.line14": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "……今、揺れた？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "...Did it just shake?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_3.line15": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "いや……たぶん気のせい――"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "No... probably just nerves—"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_3.line16": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "rumble_start"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "[Ground rumbling]"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_3.line17": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "言い終わる前に、大地が激しく震え出した。地鳴りが耳をつんざき、足元の岩が崩れる。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "地面突然剧烈震动。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "He doesn't finish before the ground erupts, the roar splitting his ears as the rock crumbles beneath him."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_3.line18": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "こちらラボ！　{name}、すぐ退避しなさい！　断層が動いてる！"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "立刻撤退，断层在动！"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lab to field! {name}, evacuate now! The fault's moving!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_3.line19": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "うわっ……！フェーズシフター……どこだっ……！"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "相位转换器在哪？快！"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Whoa...! The Phase Shifter... where is it...!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_3.line20": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "主人公は揺れる地面に足を取られながら、腰の装置を必死に掴んだ。警報音が鳴り響き、空が割れるような轟音が響く。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Staggering through the shaking, he claws for the device at his waist as alarms blare and the sky splits with thunder."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_3.line21": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "{name}ちゃん！早く！崖が――！"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "{name}! Hurry! The cliff—!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_3.line22": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "collapse_far"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "[Distant collapse]"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_3.line23": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "くそっ、頼む……作動してくれ！"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Come on, please... work!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_3.line24": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "teleport_flash"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "【传送闪光】"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "[Teleport flash]"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_3.line25": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "白い閃光が主人公を包み込む。次の瞬間、耳をつんざく地鳴りの音が消え、静寂と機械音が戻った。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "白光之后，一切安静下来。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "White light engulfs him. A heartbeat later, the deafening rumble is gone, leaving only silence and the hum of machinery."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_4.line01": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "気づけばG-Labの転送室に帰った。息が荒いまま、主人公はサンプルを机に置いた。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "回到G-Lab，把样品放好。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "When he comes to, he's back in the G-Lab transfer room, panting as he sets the sample on the table."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_4.line02": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "はぁ……はぁ……戻った……。これ……が、採ってきた薄片だよ。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "喘着气：薄片带回来了。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Hah... hah... I'm back... This is... the thin section I grabbed."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_4.line03": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "{name}ちゃん！大丈夫なの！"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "{name}，你没事吧？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "{name}! Are you okay!?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_4.line04": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "…"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "..."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_4.line05": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "……"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "……"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_4.line06": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "…………"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "………"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_4.line07": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "……怖くない先の！！"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "我没事啦。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "...I'm not scared at all!!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_4.line08": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一日中2回こんなに大きい地震遭われたなんで想像したこともないよ！"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Who could've imagined two huge quakes in a single day!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_4.line09": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "確かに大変だった……でもこの任務を実行したのが{name}てよかった。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "It was rough... but I'm glad it was you out there, {name}."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_4.line10": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "フェーズシフターを使えない人にさせたら、その結果想像したくないね。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "If we sent someone who couldn't use the Phase Shifter, I don't even want to imagine the outcome."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_4.line11": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "こんな危険な任務も無事に終えることができた、偉いぞ"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "干得漂亮。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "You wrapped up a dangerous mission. Nice work."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_4.line12": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "後はこのサンプルをちょっと研究しようか。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "接下来研究样品。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Now let's analyze the sample."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_4.line13": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "研究室のライトが点灯する映像に切り替わる。モニター越しに、顕微鏡の中の世界が広がる。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The feed shifts to the lit lab. Through the monitor, the microscopic world comes into view."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_4.line14": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "わ、すごい！粒が細かく潰れてる…これ、力がかかった跡？"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "你看，颗粒都被压扁了。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Wow, everything's crushed so fine... Is that stress marks?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_4.line15": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "そうだね。ただ、気になるのは“いつ”その力がかかったか。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Right. The question is when that stress happened."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_4.line16": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "地震のときじゃないんですか？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Wasn't it during the quake?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_4.line17": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "かもしれない。でも、この潰れ方は少し“新しすぎる”気がする。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这种压痕看起来很新。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Maybe. Yet the deformation looks a bit \"too fresh.\""
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_4.line18": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "え、新しすぎるって…どういう意味？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "What do you mean by too fresh?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_4.line19": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "地震は一度で終わったと思われているけど、もし地下のどこかがまだ動いているとしたら…。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "也许地下还在动。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "We assume the quake ended, but what if something underground is still shifting...?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_4.line20": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "……じゃあ、次に調べるのは地下、ですね？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "...Then next we investigate below ground, right?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_4.line21": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "その通り。ボーリング調査の準備をしよう。深く掘れば、“今”の地面の動きを知ることができるかもしれない。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "那就准备钻孔更深看看。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Exactly. Let's prep a boring survey. The deeper we drill, the more current movement we can read."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest3_4.line22": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "通信が切れ、山風の音だけが残った。主人公は小さく息を吐き、遠くの街を見下ろした。あの静けさの下で、地球はまだ何かを動かしているような気がした。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The call drops, leaving only mountain winds. He exhales and looks over the distant city, sensing Earth is still quietly shifting beneath the calm."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_1.line01": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ボーリングマシンの準備、完了っと！　次は{name}ちゃんのターンだね。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "钻机准备好了。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Boring rig prepped! You're up next, {name}!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_1.line02": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "……また現場行くんですか？正直、前回の崖の揺れを思い出すと足がすくむ。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "...We have to head out again? Just thinking about that cliff makes my legs shake."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_1.line03": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "怖いのはいいことだよ。慎重に動ける証拠だ。でも今回は安全装置を三重にした。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "紧张正常，我们有防护。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Being scared is good; it means you'll be careful. We've added triple safety this time."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_1.line04": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "あとフェーズシフターもアップデート済み！転送精度99.8％！"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "And the Phase Shifter's been upgraded—99.8% transfer accuracy!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_1.line05": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "0.2％の誤差がちょっと怖いけど……まあ、信じます。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "That remaining 0.2% sounds scary... but fine, I trust you."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_1.line06": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "今回掘る地点は、前回サンプルの“ずれた層”の真下。深度はおよそ50メートルだ。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这次钻到断层下约50米。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "We'll drill directly beneath the offset layer from last time, about 50 meters down."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_1.line07": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "転送装置が起動する。白い光が主人公を包み、景色が切り替わる。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "传送启动。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The transfer device fires up, white light wrapping him as the scenery shifts in a blink."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_2.line01": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "前回の露頭とは違い、地面は静まり返っていた。鳥の声もなく、風すらも薄い。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "现场安静得有点可怕。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Unlike the previous outcrop, the ground is eerily still—no birds, not even a breeze."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_2.line02": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "主人公が立つ場所は、かつて崩れた崖の少し北。そこには地震で割れた地面が乾き、まだうっすらと焦げたような色をしていた。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "He's standing just north of where the cliff collapsed; the cracked earth is dry with faint scorch marks."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_2.line03": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "……前回と空気が違うな。なんか“音”がない。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "...The air feels different. It's like the world is mute."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_2.line04": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "映像入ったよ。うわー、なんか静かすぎて逆にこわいんだけど。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Feed's in. Yikes, it's so quiet it's creepy."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_2.line05": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "今回の地点は、前回のサンプルで見つけた“ずれた層”の真上だ。あの揺れの中心に近い場所だよ。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "就在错动中心的正上方。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "This spot sits right above that shifted layer, close to the heart of the tremor."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_2.line06": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "了解。サンプルを採って戻ります。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Copy. I'll grab the samples and head back."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_2.line07": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "主人公は機材ケースを開き、装置を地面に固定した。薄暗い雲の間から、一瞬だけ光が差し込む。地表の割れ目が白く浮かび上がった。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "固定装置开始采样。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "He opens the kit, secures the device, and a sliver of light through the gray clouds highlights the fissures."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_2.line08": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "……ねえ、あの線。前より長くなってない？"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "裂缝好像变长了？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "...Hey, that line looks longer now."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_2.line09": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "気のせいじゃないかも。地面の色も違う。なんだろう、湿ってる？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Might not be your imagination. The soil looks wetter too."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_2.line10": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "地中の水分が動いてるのかもしれない。とにかく、安全第一で。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "可能是地下水在流动。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Maybe subsurface water is moving. Either way, safety first."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_2.line11": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "主人公は慎重に地表の土を取り、分析用の容器に収めた。そのとき、どこかで低い音が響いた。まるで地下の誰かが息を吐いたように。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "挖土时传来低低的声响。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "He carefully scoops the topsoil into the sample container when a low sound echoes, as if something underground sighed."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_2.line12": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "……今、聞こえました？"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "你也听到了吗？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "...Did you hear that?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_2.line13": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "うん。マイクにも入ってる。風じゃないね、これ。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Yeah, the mic picked it up too. Definitely not wind."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_2.line14": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "気をつけて。サンプルを確保したらすぐ戻ってきなさい。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Stay alert. Once it's secured, return immediately."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_2.line15": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "{name}は軽くうなずき、装置の収納を終えて、フェーズシフターを使って、GーLabに帰った。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "收好装置，返回G-Lab。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "{name} nods, packs up the gear, and activates the Phase Shifter back to G-Lab."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_3.line01": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "採取装置の振動が止まり、地中から引き上げたコアが冷たい光を放つ。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "岩芯取出来了。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The rig's vibration stops; the core pulled from underground glints coldly."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_3.line02": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "サンプル入った！推奨装置でのログも送ったよ。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sample acquired! Sent the log from the recommended unit too."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_3.line03": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "よくやったわ。その場で封じて温度を維持して。圧力データも保存しておいて。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "封存样品，把数据记下来。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Nice work. Seal it on-site and keep it at temperature; log the pressure too."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_3.line04": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "了解。帰投の準備に入る。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "明白，准备返航。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Roger. Prepping to return."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_3.line05": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "冷却ファンの音だけが静かに響き、空は薄く色づいていた。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Only the cooling fans whisper while the sky blushing faintly overhead."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_4.line01": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "おかえり！今度は崖に落ちたりしてないよね？"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "欢迎回来，平安就好。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Welcome back! You didn't fall off a cliff, right?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_4.line02": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "あはは、ギリギリセーフ。靴が泥だらけになったけどね。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Haha, barely. My boots are mud again though."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_4.line03": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "無事で何より。フェーズシフターの転送データも問題なさそうだ。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Glad you're safe. Phase Shifter logs look clean too."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_4.line04": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "これが、今日のサンプルです。ちょっと変な感触があったけど……"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "样品触感有点怪。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Here's the sample. Felt kind of odd, though..."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_4.line05": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "そう、じゃあさっそく見てみようか。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "I see. Let's take a look."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_4.line06": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "サンプルが分析台の上に置かれ、静かにスキャナーの光が走った。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The sample rests on the analyzer as scanner light sweeps by."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_4.line07": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "……見て先生、この層。下の方だけ粒が潰れてる。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "下层颗粒都被压扁了。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "...Look, Sensei, down here. Only the lower grains got crushed."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_4.line08": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ほんとだ……しかも粒の向きがそろっている。地層が横に“動かされた”跡だ。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "是横向挤压的痕迹。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "You're right... and the grains align. Classic lateral shearing."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_4.line09": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "つまり、地面の下で何かが滑った？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "So something beneath the surface slipped?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_4.line10": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "そう。そしてそれは、地震直後のサンプルにはなかった変化だ。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Exactly—and we didn't see this right after the quake."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_4.line11": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ってことは……ここ、今も動いてるの？"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "说明地下还在动？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Then does that mean it's still moving?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_4.line12": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "モニターに映るデータが小さく震えた。画面のラインがゆっくりと歪み、赤いエリアが広がる。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The data on the monitor trembles, the graph warps, and red zones widen."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_4.line13": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "……これは断層の“呼吸”だ。仙台の地下、眠っていないかも。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这像是断层在“呼吸”。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "...That's the fault \"breathing.\" The ground under Sendai might not be asleep."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_4.line14": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "……断層が、動いてる……？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "...The fault is alive...?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_4.line15": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "“呼吸する断層”っていうのはね、地表では静かに見えても、地下でまだ力を溜めたり緩めたりしている“活断層”のことよ。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "活断层表面平静，地下却在活动。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "A \"breathing fault\" looks calm on the surface but still loads and releases stress underneath—it's active."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_4.line16": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "何年、何十年も動かないこともあるけど、確かに“生きている”。だからこそ、次の一瞬を油断できないの。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "It might lie dormant for decades but it's still alive, so we can't let our guard down."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_4.line17": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "……地面が生きてるって、やっぱり怖いけど、どこか切ないね。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "...The earth feeling alive is both terrifying and a little heartbreaking."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_4.line18": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "部屋の空気が一瞬止まった。窓の外では、夕陽がビルの隙間に沈みかけていた。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The room goes still as the sunset sinks between the buildings outside."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_4.line19": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "しかし、今、地層の下は一体どのようなのか……これを証明するため、もっとはっきりな情報が必要だ"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "我们还需要更确切的情报。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Still, we need clearer data to prove what's happening beneath these strata."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_4.line20": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "地表からの観測だけでは、もう限界ね。断層の“呼吸”はさらに深いところで起きているかもしれない。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Surface observations alone won't cut it anymore. The \"breathing\" may be deeper down."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_4.line21": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "つまり、次は地下を“見る”ってことですか？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "So next we literally look underground?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_4.line22": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "そう。人が入れない場所を調べるには、機械の目が必要。――無人探査ドローンを使おう。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "用无人机去探查。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Right. Places people can't reach need mechanical eyes—unmanned probe drones."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_4.line23": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ドローンで断層を探るって、ちょっとワクワクするね……でも、危なくない？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Using drones to chase faults sounds exciting... but is it safe?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_4.line24": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "リスクがないとは言えないけれど、実際今回の任務は採集任務より安全だよ、野外に行く必要は無いから。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Can't say zero risk, but it's safer than field sampling—you won't have to go outside."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_4.line25": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "でも、今回の任務も大事だよ。いろんな人の命を救えるかもしれない。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "任务仍然很重要。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "But this mission is just as important; it could save lives too."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest4_4.line26": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "三人の視線がモニターの地図に集まる。赤いラインが、仙台の地下を静かに走っていた――その線の先に、まだ知られざる真実が眠っている。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "视线落在地图上的断层红线。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "All three gaze at the red line on the map, stretching beneath Sendai as if guarding untold truths."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_1.line01": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "夜のG-Lab。窓の外では雨が降り出していた。雷が遠くで光り、モニターの青い光が室内を照らす。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "夜雨和闪电笼罩着G-Lab。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Night settles over G-Lab as rain starts outside; distant lightning flashes while monitor glow bathes the lab."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_1.line02": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "新しいドローンの準備できたよ。これは普通のドローンじゃないよ。“地中レーダー群システム”、試作一号。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "地下雷达群无人机就绪。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The new drone unit is ready. It's not a normal drone—it's the Phase Radar Swarm prototype."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_1.line03": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "地中レーダー群？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Phase radar swarm?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_1.line04": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "そう。小型ドローンを十数体、裂け目や水路に潜り込ませて、電磁波で地下構造を可視化する装置だ。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "无人机将进入裂隙描绘结构。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Right. A dozen mini drones slip into cracks and waterways, mapping underground structures with EM waves."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_1.line05": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "つまり、地面の“中身”をスキャンできるってこと！まるで地球のCTスキャンだね。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "就像给地球做CT。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "So basically we can scan the inside of the earth! Like a planetary CT."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_1.line06": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "……すごい。じゃあ本当に、断層の形が見える？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "...That's amazing. So we'll actually see the fault's shape?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_1.line07": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "理論上はね。ただ、送る波が強すぎると地下の水分に反射されてノイズが出る。慎重に扱ってくれ。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "In theory. But if the signal's too strong, groundwater reflects it and adds noise, so be careful."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_1.line08": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "{name}くん、今回ドローンの操作をよろしく"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "{name}，这次由你来操作。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "{name}, we're counting on you to pilot them."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_1.line09": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "了解……ちょっと、この十数体のドローンが私一人で操作するの？"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "十几架都要我控？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Got it... Wait, I have to control all dozen by myself?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_1.line10": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "もちろん、やってみよう！"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Of course. Let's give it a shot!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_1.line11": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "（心声）kaede先生、強引すぎだな……"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "(Inner voice) Kaede-sensei is so pushy..."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_1.line12": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "……今、揺れた？"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "……又晃了一下？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "...Did the ground just shake?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_2.line01": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ドローン起動シークエンス、開始。十数体の小型ドローンが青い光を点滅させながら、ゆっくりと浮かび上がった。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "无人机启动升空。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Drone activation sequence start. A dozen mini drones blink blue as they rise."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_2.line02": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "わぁ……すごい。まるで群れで飛ぶ蛍みたい……。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Wow... gorgeous. Like a flock of fireflies."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_2.line03": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ほんとだ。これ全部、俺たちが操縦するのか……ちょっと緊張してきたな。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Totally. Can't believe we're flying all of them... I'm nervous now."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_2.line04": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ふふ、指揮官デビューだね。落とさないようにね？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Hehe, commander debut. Don't crash them, okay?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_2.line05": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "冗談はそのくらいにして。ドローン群、地中レーダーシステムのリンクを開始する。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "雷达系统连线完成。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Jokes aside. Drone swarm, begin linking to the subsurface radar system."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_2.line06": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "モニターに十数本の通信ラインが走り、ドローンが次々と地面の裂け目へと滑り込んでいく。青い光がひとつ、またひとつ、地中に消えていった――。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "无人机进入裂隙下潜。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Communication lines streak across the monitors as each drone slips into cracks, their blue lights disappearing underground."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_2.line07": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "まずはドローン1から8、信号確認。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Checking signals from drones 1 through 8 first."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_2.line08": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "深度10メートル……15……あれ、9番がノイズ出してる！"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Depth 10 meters... 15... Uh-oh, drone 9's throwing noise!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_2.line09": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "映像、出てます！……これ、なに？　赤い線みたいなのが地面の下を走ってる。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "地下出现一条红线。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Feed's up! ...What is that? A red line running under the ground?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_2.line10": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "……それが断層面だ。だけど、想定よりずっと浅い。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "那是断层面，比预想浅。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "...That's the fault plane. But it's way shallower than expected."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_2.line11": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "浅いってことは……都市の地下施設と近いってこと！？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "If it's that shallow... doesn't that put it near the city's infrastructure?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_2.line12": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "モニターの映像が切り替わる。仙台の地図が投影され、断層の線がゆっくりと街の下を横切っていく。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "地图显示断层贯穿城市。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The display switches to a Sendai map, fault lines crawling beneath the city."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_2.line13": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "……これ……仙台駅の真下まで伸びてる。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "...It stretches all the way under Sendai Station."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_2.line14": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "しかも線が途中で枝分かれしてるよ！二本？いや、三本？"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "断层在多处分岔。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "And it branches! Two lines? No, three?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_2.line15": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "……分岐断層か。これほど広範囲に広がっているとは……。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "...Branch faults. I didn't expect them to spread this far..."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_2.line16": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "モニターの波形が一瞬跳ね上がった。赤い警告が点灯する。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The waveform suddenly spikes and red alerts flash."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_2.line17": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "なにこれ！？波が動いてる！……リアルタイムで！"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "断层正在实时活动。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "What is that!? The waveform's moving—in real time!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_2.line18": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "まさか……まだ滑っているのか！？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "No way... is it still slipping!?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_2.line19": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "待って……先生、これ、地震計の信号に似てます。しかも周期が短い。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Hold on... Sensei, it looks like a seismogram, and the period's short."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_2.line20": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "周期が短い……つまり、応力が“蓄積”している。これは……前兆じゃない。次の震動が“始まっている”。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "应力在快速累积。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "A short period means stress is building. This isn't a warning—it's the next quake beginning."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_2.line21": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "モニターの地図に、仙台全域を覆うように赤い線が広がった。その中心に、“G-Lab”の位置が点滅する。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "红线扩散，G-Lab在中心。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "On the map, the red lines spread across Sendai with G-Lab blinking at the center."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_2.line22": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "うそ……私たち、断層の真上にいるの！？"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "No way... we're right on top of the fault!?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_2.line23": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "……G-Labだけじゃない。仙台市の主要エリア全体が、いま動こうとしている断層の上にある。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "主要城区都在断层上。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "...Not just G-Lab. All of central Sendai is sitting on this awakening fault."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_2.line24": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "じゃあ……これから来るのは、本震……。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "本震要来了。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Then... the next thing coming is the main shock..."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_2.line25": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "雷鳴が鳴り響いた。窓の外の雨が急に強くなる。ラボの明かりが一瞬、落ちた。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Thunder cracks and rain lashes harder outside as the lab lights flicker."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_2.line26": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "……みんな、聞いてくれ。これ以上は隠せない。政府にも、そして市民にも知らせる必要がある。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "必须告知政府和市民。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "...Everyone, listen. We can't hide this anymore. We have to tell the government and the public."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_2.line27": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "そうですね、これは、みんなの命を救う研究だよ！"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Exactly. This research can save lives!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_2.line28": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "……わかりました。次の任務は、“知らせること”。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "下一任务：对外告知。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "...Understood. Our next mission is to warn them."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "story.quest5_2.line29": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "三人は無言で頷き合った。モニターには、まだ脈打つように光る赤い断層の線が残っていた。まるで地球が、ゆっくりと息をしているかのように。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "红线仍在脉动。"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The three nod in silence. On the monitor, the pulsing red fault line glows as if the earth itself is breathing."
          }
        }
      }
    },
